(42, 'Top 10 Digital Marketing Tools for Businesses', 'Hyderabad', '<p>The World is a digital globe, with everyone connected on the network today. With the fast-emerging technologies, the world is becoming smaller by the day. Digital Marketing has become the need of the hour, for businesses to flourish as nearly 60% of the world population is active on social media. There are many tools that have been developed to improve businesses digitally, from the comfort of one&rsquo;s home. The <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>Top 10 Digital Marketing Tools for Businesses</strong></a> have been identified in this blog post for the easy understanding and implementation of the same for improving your business prospects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For many of us, Google has been the starting point of any technology that we see online today. Right from the search engine to its latest Google Home, Google has always been revolutionary in innovating new approaches to technology. Likewise, Google has many free online tools for a smooth butter-like function of your business. With many <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>types of digital marketing tools</strong></a> in the market, Google stands tall among the best. Here are a few of the <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best digital marketing tools of 2021</strong></a> listed for your understanding and information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Google Analytics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>First and foremost, let us all agree on a point that Google has been the frontrunner in technology and so have been its <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>digital marketing tools for businesses</strong></a>. Google Analytics is a completely <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>free digital marketing tool</strong></a> that gives you a comprehensive analysis of how many visitors you have for your website and with which content they engage more. This will give you an idea of the areas you have to improve and the strong points that you have. This information helps you optimize your website content and then plan a marketing strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Google Search Console</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When paired with Google Analytics, Google Search Console helps you identify any problems on your site and optimize its traffic. The insights provided by Google Search Console about the traffic generated and the content optimization of your website, best describe its efficiency as a digital marketing tool. Working with Google Analytics in association with the Search Console will drastically improve the numbers of your site in turn improving your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Google Adwords</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Among the <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best free digital marketing tools for entrepreneurs</strong></a>, Google Adwords ranks among the best. This easy-to-use tool has a keyword planner which lets you know the SEO rankings of the keyword, then also lets you choose relevant keywords that rank better. Google Adwords is one of the <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best digital marketing tools</strong></a> that lets you identify, plan and optimize your web content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yoast</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is no point in spending hours together researching keywords and then not optimize your content with them. Yoast lets you do just that. It is the most efficient SEO tool that optimizes your web content and its free version is absolutely resourceful. The Yoast tool will tell you where to place the keywords, how to optimize your website &amp; blog and how to improve readability. You can also add related keywords, get instant keyword suggestions, insights, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; UberSuggest</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This digital marketing tool is easy for beginners and offers what most paid tools give for a price. UberSuggest provides useful keyword information such as total search volume, difficulty, and paid difficulty for running an ad campaign around that keyword. You also get the keyword ideas and suggestions related to the one you are searching for. You can update your older content or develop a content marketing plan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Canva</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Canva is a design tool that lets you access 50000+ design templates for your social media. You need to keep your audience engaged with your designs. With each passing day, you can see that the designs are evolving and new designs are uploaded each day. You don&rsquo;t need to have any design experience to work on Canva. Each design is carefully crafted so that you just need to place your content and watch it take shape right before your eyes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MailChimp</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eight out of Ten marketers use e-mail marketing while launching a business. Mail Chimp is one of the <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best e-mail marketing tools</strong></a> there is. Initially, your business may not have more than 2000 subscribers. Till that point, you can use this tool for free and as you scale up you can opt for a paid plan. MailChimp has been the most trusted <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>e-mail marketing tool</strong></a> since 2001 with more than 11&nbsp; million subscribers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For an initial setup of your business, it is free for up to 2000 contacts. You can send 300 e-mails per day for free. MailChimp is one of the <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best digital marketing tools for businesses</strong></a> and start-ups.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hubspot</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hubspot is a marketing software that leaves no stone unturned in SEO. The following are the services provided by HubSpot for the convenience of businesses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Blogging</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SEO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Social Media</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Website</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lead Management</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Landing Pages</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Calls-to-action</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; E-mail marketing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Marketing Automation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Analytics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; With everything you need to improve your business, there is no need to get pulled in the many directions of the different tools there are on the web. HubSpot is the one thing you need that provides all the digital marketing solutions in one place.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BuzzSumo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>BuzzSumo is a <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>content marketing tool</strong></a> that helps you schedule your content and analyze the results. BuzzSumo is a tool that you can use to search viral posts and trending content online. It also offers <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>digital marketing tools</strong></a> like:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Keyword Research</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Influencer Search</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Content Analysis</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Crisis Management</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Brand Monitoring Tools</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Topic-based social media feeds, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10.&nbsp; HootSuite</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>Social Media Marketing</strong></a> playing a major role in the digital marketing scenario, HootSuite becomes necessary to manage all your social media platforms in one place. It allows you to respond to comments, react to stories, post automated responses and social media posts. You can also get advanced reporting tools for Social Media Campaigns and get feedback after each campaign. <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>Social Media Marketing</strong></a> becomes easy with tools like HootSuite where you can manage up to 30 social media platforms.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These are some of the <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best digital marketing tools of 2021</strong></a> that have made their mark in the online market. However, there is one grand tool that does it all. The Google pack. The all-encompassing Google suite is the go-to tool for all our digital needs. Right from preparing docs or sheets to sharing them on the drive, Google has made it easy to perform all tasks digitally and online. Now the need to mail a document after you prepare it has been done with as you can now prepare and keep all your data online and within reach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The revolutionary <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>digital marketing tools</strong></a> which have been mentioned above have proved to be useful to many beginners, start-ups, entrepreneurs, and even established businesses. With the advent of online marketing, everything is now bought and sold online which is facilitated by <a href=\"http://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>digital marketing tools</strong></a> for promotion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Creating a strong digital marketing strategy is essential for a business to flourish in the current scenario, one that includes e-mail marketing, SEO, Social Media Marketing, Content Management. For any business to succeed, finding the right digital marketing tools and using them consistently is the key.</p>\r\n', '02-Aug-2021', 'top-10-digital-marketing-tools-for-businesses', '1900.jpeg', '', '', ''),
(43, 'The Future of Digital Marketing in India', 'Hyderabad', '<p>India has one of the largest populations of internet users in the world. The future of digital marketing in India seems bright and fruitful. A survey by Goldman Sachs suggested that almost 980 million internet users and out of that nearly 666 million users of digital market will be present by 2025 and the market is valued at $160 billion. The digital presence of your brand and its saleability will increase 10-fold in the near future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">Digital marketing</a> is the art of promoting your products or services on digital media. Companies and business are starting to take advantage of this vast medium to reach their millions of customers and clients through ways of TV, Internet- social media particularly. This has become much easier as the internet access has increased globally and the penetration of smart phones into every nook and corner of the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Businesses can identify their potential customers, build a brand, market their product or service, deliver their goods and services, and get feedback on a regular basis. All this can be done digitally with the help of internet and social media.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Digital marketers can channel their <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">marketing strategies on social media</a>, through email, search engines and websites. The first thing that made digital marketing a success is the number of customers businesses can reach. This has been increasing drastically with each day. The penetration of the internet too has reached extraordinary numbers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A study shows that the search rate for the term &ldquo;digital marketing&rdquo; has increased during the pandemic lockdown. This shows that the people are realizing the importance of digital marketing for their businesses as well as personal growth. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The major contributors for the growth of <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">digital marketing</a> are the small enterprises, start-ups and budding entrepreneurs. In light of COVID-19, entrepreneurs are more inclined to market their products the digital marketing way instead of personal visits. The growth of digital marketing has seen an upward trend and this also seems to be holding true for the near future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The growth of digital marketing has been very gradual though dramatic in India. More opportunities come up each day expanding the scope of digital marketing in India. People are adapting to the new normal and the growth of internet we have seen the past few years is here to stay. We are now used to do everything online from shopping groceries, medicines to bank transactions and even house purchases today.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The future is digital, hence adapting to the changes gradually is necessary for all of to have a hassle-free life in the future. To be able to deliver to our customers online will be our forte in the coming days. Digital marketing experts are needed for every business to cater to their specific needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Businesses in India are becoming digitally equipped to cater to the market needs. Many of them are investing in digital marketing to gain a strong foothold in the market against their competitors. Digital marketing techniques are affordable and cost-effective. The campaigns run can be monitored on a minute-to-minute basis and the progress can be assessed in a certain manner. This gives the added advantage of monitoring leads into conversions. The effectiveness of each marketing campaign can be analysed thoroughly to improve in the next one. The results in digital marketing are measurable which is difficult in traditional marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">Digital marketing</a> has many different aspects like content marketing, <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">social media marketing</a>, <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">search engine optimisation</a>, finance and business development. Analysing every aspect of digital marketing offers a road map to further improvisation in strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The previous traditional marketing set up was limited to door to door and mouth publicity. But the new Gen Z want everything on their fingertips. Fulfilling the needs of the customers is the highest priority of digital marketers. Even the smallest requirements of the customers need to taken care of. Making campaigns and writing engaging content is the need of the hour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With everyone preferring digital marketing over everything else, it has become the most powerful tool in the hands of the marketers. Opting for Digital marketing is the best decision that marketers are making today. Every type of product or service can be marketed using digital marketing techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The government&rsquo;s digital marketing initiatives like the Digital India have given a boost to the start ups and budding entrepreneurs looking to expand their scope of business. Turning India into a digitally empowered country and a knowledge economy has been the goal of the government by giving a boost to the country&rsquo;s small businesses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The government&rsquo;s e-marketplace marketed as GeM has been bringing enterprises together onto a platform and giving them the acquaintance needed for digital empowerment. The youth of the country are particularly being encouraged to enrol new businesses on the platform and participate in the bidding processes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Go Digital, Go Global&rdquo; is the new mantra of the small as well as large businesses. Through platforms like Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and LinkedIn we can reach any corner of the world and this gives an added advantage to those live on these platforms. The reach of social media is so huge that its potential to give a boost to businesses is endless.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The government&rsquo;s initiatives like the Smart Cities mission are turning the potential towns also into smart cities with equipment installed at every corner. Many start-ups are getting lunched in tier-II and tier-III towns and they have global outreach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since people are spending an average of 2 hrs a day on social media, it is an engaging medium which constantly attracts attention of the user. It has been surveyed that the revenue generated through digital media is going to be five-fold than it was in 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The scope for <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">digital marketing</a> is wider than what it was previously. It is the most powerful and will be the most powerful tool in the hands of businesses and to boost their reach and in turn the sales. The dynamics of the market keep changing, so should the marketing techniques. With the ever-increasing demand in the services and products online, a change in attitude and aptitude for digital marketing will take your business forward. So, if you&rsquo;re thinking of going digital, now is the time. There is a vast scope for improvement and there is a huge gap between the market and supply. If this needs to be fulfilled, stepping in fully equipped with digital platforms is necessary. This will give you a competitive edge over the other competitors and you will reign the market for a very long time.</p>\r\n', '21-Aug-2021', 'the-future-of-digital-marketing-in-india', '1944.jpeg', '', '', ''),
(44, 'B2B Digital Marketing Strategies', 'Hyderabad', '<p>Digital marketing can be as simple as it seems at the same time as difficult if not understood properly. There are different approaches and modules to digital marketing. You should understand the modules of digital marketing before targeting the audiences. Marketing to different businesses is different from marketing to individuals. Approaches to <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>B2B digital marketing strategy </strong></a>must be on-point. For a better understanding of <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>B2B digital marketing strategy</strong></a>, let us delve deeper into this article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>#What is B2B digital marketing strategy?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>B2B marketing refers to any marketing strategy that is directed towards businesses. Any organization that markets products or services uses digital marketing. The <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>B2B digital marketing strategy</strong></a> targets the requirements, and interests of customers of a business organization. The purchase motivation of customers in a B2B strategy is logic and financial incentive and they want to be properly educated about the business&rsquo;s products and services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In a <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>B2B digital marketing strategy</strong></a>, there are different strategies that need to be understood properly. Here are the stages involved in the marketing strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Awareness Stage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The customer is experiencing a turbulent atmosphere. They are trying to decide whether or not they are going to opt for a particular product or service. They are trying to educate themselves and arrive at a decision soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Consideration Stage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The customer has fully researched the product or service. They are considering different options and are soon going to arrive at a decision.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Decision Stage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The customer has now decided on their strategy, approach or method. They have compiled a list of all prospective vendors or service providers and they are ready to finalize from the list.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong># B2B Email Marketing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Email Marketing is a tried and tested method for digital marketing. Almost 93% of B2B marketers use email marketing. Emails turn leads into potential customers. Email Marketing is a powerful tool for making your brand reachable to all target audiences. Here are some ways to improve your email marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Writing powerful email content</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Giving a pin-pointed Call-to-Action (CTA)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Target your emails to the most appropriate or relevant audience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Responsive email designs grab the audience&rsquo;s attention</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Try to convert new leads into customers through cold mail</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong># B2B Digital Marketing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best digital marketing strategy</strong></a> involves some nuances which can be relevant to improving your brand. Every business should have a digital presence that will help target potential customers. Digital marketing has become a new tool for businesses to improve their potential. Defining your target audience is the first step to a successful digital marketing strategy. Create an interactive website that is rich in user experience. Optimize your digital presence with on-page and off-page SEO. Use PPC marketing for better reach and targeting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong># B2B Content Marketing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Content marketing supports digital marketing in all the modules. Content marketing involves not just content creation but also anticipating what your audience is searching for and giving them what they need. B2B marketing involves educating customers, which can be possible only with the creation of engaging content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong># B2B Social Media Marketing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social Media Marketing is not just for B2C marketing, it is most useful for B2B marketing as well. Here&rsquo;s how you can optimize your social media marketing for targeting a specific audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Build Brand Awareness</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Build an online personality for your company</p>\r\n\r\n<p>â—&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Humanizing your business</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>B2B digital marketing strategies</strong></a> have not been very successful as they are not planned to target a specific audience. Developing a strategy will offer a competitive advantage over the other competitors. Create a customer-centric website to engage your audiences. Help your audience to learn and work smarter by creating engaging content. Identify your strengths and weaknesses with competitive analysis tools. Now you can optimize your strategy to suit your analysis and improve where you can.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keep a track of all your steps and also the best digital marketing strategies of your competitors. Test new methods and tweak them if necessary, to suit your needs. It is never too late to start on a digital marketing journey for your B2B marketing. It helps in identifying the potential customers and retain them for a very long association.</p>\r\n', '29-August-2021', 'b2b-digital-marketing-strategies', '1985.jpeg', '', '', ''),
