(64, 'Why Social Media is Important To Increase Traffic to Your Website?', 'Hyderabad', '<p>In the world that&#39;s rapidly modernizing, business and marketing too is evolving and changing. There are so many platforms, agencies and their strategies emerging to keep up with the new world. To keep up with that and survive in the business market you must get on board so that your marketing methods do not get outdated.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One such strategy among different kind of <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>digital marketing services</strong></a> is the use of social media. Social media, these days, are highly important and highly preferable because it makes it possible for companies to connect one on one with its target audience and transform those audiences into possible customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To know why <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>social media marketing</strong></a> is important keep reading. Social media contributes largely in a brand&#39;s ability to generate brand awareness and online growth. With our social media marketing tools and advertising services you business can grow globally and also generate leads. Reaching your audiences is super easy no matter what location they are in. <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>ASE TECHNOLOGIES</strong></a> believe in. transforming your audiences into prospective consumers with our <strong><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">social media marketing agency</a>. </strong>When a marketing firm uses social media to connect with its audiences it generates awareness, leads, sales and revenue.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social Media is Important for your business for a number of reasons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Driving Traffic -</strong> One of your goals must</p>\r\n\r\n<p>be to drive traffic and achieve that, social media is a great digital strategy. Since half the population is on phone for the most part of their day you must be wanting them to click through your website and engage with it. Like other digital marketing tools social media can increase website traffic and engage audiences in ways that would convert them into possible clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Prospecting - </strong>Social media has a different impact compared to all other digital marketing techniques. Social media offers the opportunity to get in front of a larger referral audience organically when followers engage with content making it show up in their networks&rsquo; feeds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Brand&#39;s Reputation - </strong>When your clients visit your website, some of them leave reviews, good or bad, that you may take sincerely to provide them what is required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These feedbacks help you build your brand&#39;s reputation. When other consumers go through these websites they might find you worthy of their interests, increasing your leads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Growth -</strong> As more people today are on the internet it becomes easy for you to grow your business in a virtual world like this. By engaging a larger target audience you create brand awareness that help you generate leads thereby bringing in higher revenues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter you run a small scale business or a large scale business social media contributes equally to both. It has a lot of potential for generating growth and fulfilling your business goals. For different <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>social</strong> <strong>media</strong> <strong>marketing</strong> <strong>services</strong></a> reach out to ASE TECHNOLOGIES as we provide you strategies ensuring guaranteed growth leaving positive impact on your clients.</p>\r\n', '03-January-2022', 'why-social-media-is-important-to-increase-traffic-to-your-website', 'asetech14.jpg', '', '', ''),
(65, 'How to improve the ranking of your website on search engines?', 'Hyderabad', '<p>Have you ever wondered where does all the traffic come from? How do people get to know about you? The magical yet practical factor working behind this is Search Engine Optimization more popularly known as SEO. You will find many <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>SEO Agencies in India</strong></a> giving you these services. Your business isn&rsquo;t likely to grow if nobody actually finds you. To be able to generate leads people should be able to find you easily and also before they find someone else. You must have come across the phrase &ldquo;first impression is the last impression&rdquo;. Similarly, that which is easily visible or discoverable to the audiences are most eligible of gaining public attention. The results that appear on the top on search engines are most likely to be clicked by the audiences. In other words, if you do not occupy the top position on the page you&rsquo;re most likely to miss the attention of the potential customers. Most of the audiences do not even bother to go to the second page. Taking measures to improve your SEO can help your website rank higher. If you&rsquo;re not doing well on the SEO rankings, its never too late to get it done right. There are a few ways to increase your chances of rising up the ranking list.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some ways to improve your SEO rankings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Increase Page Loading</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If your loading speed is not fast enough, the search engines will recognize it and affect your ranking. The website visitors wouldn&rsquo;t engage much with your page if the speed is relatively slow. All this will affect your ranking largely. When a particular page takes more than 3 seconds to load, half the website visitors prefer leaving the page. Once they leave the page, they wouldn&rsquo;t even consider returning to it since they have already formed an impression of the page by then. This affects your SEO ranking terribly. When your website loads faster people keep coming back. To provide you the best digital marketing services there are <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>SEO</strong> <strong>Services</strong></a> spread all over India. Among the <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best SEO services companies</strong> <strong>in India</strong></a> ASE TECHNOLOGIES is one that you must not miss upon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>High Quality Content</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Updating your website is important to improve your SEO ranking. You won&rsquo;t have a great SEO ranking if you haven&rsquo;t modified it since the day you first built it. Visitors need a reason to keep coming back to your website and only the interesting ones would gather more traffic. Relevant and interesting contents are likely to fetch more attention. Contents with high quality drives more traffic to your website. The more time the website visitors spend on your page the more advantages you gain. Fresh and attractive contents keep them engaged to your page. You&rsquo;ll find multiple number of companies claiming to be the <strong><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">best SEO agency in India</a>. </strong>Do not get misguided by them and choose from the best <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>SEO services in India</strong></a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Blogging</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Blogging helps your website largely. It is a great tool to generate leads. Blogging doesn&rsquo;t just engage visitors to your website. It also improves your SEO rankings. If readers find your blogs interesting they&rsquo;ll regularly visit your website which will increase the dwell time of your page and increase your ranking. All these work towards improving your search engine rankings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Adding More Than Just Texts</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have just written words on your website, it is more likely to bore your potential clients. You can add many more things to your website other than just texts. Pictures are one thing. You can also add videos, slide shows, etc. that will attract customers and increase your website traffic. Clients want to watch more videos because they find videos more appealing than reading. This can drastically increase the time one spends on your website. This definitely helps in boosting your search ranking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Share On Social Media</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is so much important for websites to be active on social media. When people share links to your website on social media, your SEO ranking improves, and not everybody knows about it. If you engage in sharing your links regularly on social media pages, it will contribute largely to your website traffic. Just one click from the possible clients and a little bit improvement in your ranking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SEO is something that&rsquo;s going to last for quite some time in the digital market. Therefore, concentrating on it in present as well as future is important to grow your business. If you follow these steps who knows you might come to occupy the top spot. To make your way towards the top search results these are steps that are unavoidable.</p>\r\n', '10-January-2022', 'how-to-improve-the-ranking-of-your-website-on-search-engines', 'asetech16.jpg', '', '', ''),
(66, 'How Long Tail Keywords Enhance Your Business Growth?', 'Hyderabad', '<p>Before diving right in we would explain you what <strong><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">long tail keywords</a> </strong>are. When four words or more are clubbed together to form a term, it is categorized as long tail keyword. Since these consist of more words they are more descriptive and specific. <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>Long tail keywords</strong></a> give more information compared to short ones. For your clarity, go through the examples below:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Short term keywords &ndash; <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>SEO services</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Long term keywords &ndash; S<a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">EO services in Vizag</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rooting for long tail keywords is a great way to engage traffic to your website. Let us now look at the advantages of incorporating <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>long tail keywords</strong></a> within your SEO strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lower Level of Competitions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Search engine optimization has evolved to be the popular digital marketing strategy. We can call it a mainstream marketing activity and if you&rsquo;re wondering what main stream activity is then let us make it clear to you that it is something that&rsquo;s utilised by all sectors of marketing. All the marketing units or business firms prefers using SEO services in order to strategize their marketing system. Every marketing firm has a target market who they aim to convert. To get them converted to possible customers you have to go where they go, search exactly what they search and the attempt to rank for those specific keywords. Since all organizations do not prefer long tail keywords it&rsquo;s an opportunity for you to grab to gain maximum number of customer attention.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>70% Search Terms Are Long Tail Keywords</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most searches on the search engines are of four words or more. You must now realize how important long tail keywords are to match up with those searches. It is because the search engines now focus on what we want it&rsquo;s easy for them to guess what&rsquo;s on our head. We can now search any complicated terms using the number of words we feel comfortable with and they&rsquo;ll still match up to our wants and this is all because of these long tail keywords that come under SEO services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Know Your Searcher&rsquo;s Intent</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When a long tail keyword is typed into a search engine it becomes easy to understand what they want. Long tail keywords are descriptive and gives us specific information about what the user wants and in this way it gets simpler for companies to give them the results they&rsquo;re actually looking for. From this, we can see just how useful long-tail keywords are in their ability to sort the potential clients from the browsers. Make sure you are answering questions that your target audience has, thereby creating valuable content and giving them great ease in travelling through your conversion funnel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Helps You Appear In Voice Searches</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Voice search has been growing mostly over the years. People using voice search mostly uses long tail keywords as they look for answer to their specific questions. Having additional keywords in your content will increase our chances of ranking for these queries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The use of long tail keywords together with other strategies will help support SEO efforts. Long tail keywords give you chances and makes it possible for you to connect with your customer on a deeper level by answering their questions. To connect with your target audience, you&rsquo;d find more than one <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>best SEO</strong> <strong>services</strong> <strong>agencies</strong></a> in India that wouldn&rsquo;t only provide you amazing strategies but would ensure your growth on a digital platform. To have the most <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>affordable SEO</strong> <strong>services</strong></a> why not get in touch with one of the best SEO services company in Vizag, known as ASE TECHNOLOGIES.</p>\r\n', '17-January-2022', 'how-long-tail-keywords-enhance-your-business-growth', 'asetech18.jpg', '', '', ''),
