(72, '5 Pros and Cons of Social media marketing in business', 'Hyderabad', '<p>In case you&#39;re stepping forward to a digital marketing plan let me introduce you to the main advantages of <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>social media marketing</strong></a>, in other words, social media marketing benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Using social media you can reach your target audience anytime and also stay connected with them. This is one of the most obvious social media marketing advantages. Half of world&#39;s population is into social media, which makes it one of the most advantageous platform for <strong><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">digital marketing</a>. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Through social media posts you have high chances of having your content go viral. Besides that, you can also benefit from user generated content. Through this users make content without having you participated. This saves you a lot of time. This also acts as a very strong social proof.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Using social media you can easily find out what users really think of you with the help of social media monitoring tools. It helps you to know more about the user&#39;s sentiments related to your product or service. You can always find out what users think of your brand and you also can keep a track of your user&#39;s perception of your brand compared to your competitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. It is only through social media that you get familiarized with trends and hot topics for discussion. It is one of the best social media marketing advantages to promote and enhance your brand digitally. With Hashtagify and Google Trends you can find the most trending hashtags for Instagram and Twitter&nbsp;and also discover trendy topics for your SMM posts. By analyzing this given data, you can come up with ideas of your own to engage with possible clients and make them participate in your discussion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. The most convenient and most innovative way to engage with audiences is the use of social media. Users have an easy access to connect with a brand or company through social media, which saves them the time and effort of calling the support team or mailing them personally. Introducing a chat bot is way more helpful as customers expect expect responses at least within an hour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social Media has both advantages and disadvantages, and thus, the blog here covers the topic social media marketing advantages and disadvantages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. When you use social media to promote your brands or services, you get to know a little too much about human nature. You also learn that users won&#39;t always respond positively. As long as you do them good toh can expect good, in case they don&#39;t like anything be ready to face the lows. At least that&#39;s what social media analytics say. You can satisfy people, and that&#39;s right, but if you think you can satisfy everybody then you&#39;re mistaken because you cannot. Each negative review if seen by your current customers you&#39;ll definitely lose them with utmost possibility. But what you can do here to save yourself is look into the review your clients give and then go stay fixing it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Contents on social media are innumerable. Therefore there&#39;s a high chance for customers and clients to get bored. So what can keep them interested is anything new. In order to engage customers continuously you will have to come up with something new almost every day. You may have to go live, post new contents, share jokes or anything that can generate leads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. There&#39;s no prohibition when it comes to a small scale business or a large scale. Basically the size of your business doesn&#39;t impact your goals. But what impacts is the kind or type of business you&#39;re into. Since some of the hashtags are prohibited to be used, so if your product or service falls under these hashtags you may not be able to gain a wider audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. You cannot reach all segments of users. Since everyone is not good with what you&#39;re good at they may expect something else for them to deal better.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Advertising on social media can be really expensive. It can save you money only if you can set your social media marketing campaigns correctly. In the event of a mistake with the target audience, region, or language of the advertising campaign, there are big risks that waste your social media marketing budget and get zero ROI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just how there exists social media marketing benefits, so does the drawbacks of it. Therefore to business digitally and successfully you got to overcome the hurdles and makes your way out by multiplying the benefits. Our <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>social media marketing agency</strong></a>, ASE TECHNOLOGIES, knows how to deal with modern users and turn them into possible prospects.</p>\r\n', '28-February-2022', '5-pros-and-cons-of-social-media-marketing-in-business', 'ase27.jpg', '', '', ''),
(73, 'SEARCH ENGINE MARKETING | IMPORTANCE OF SEARCH ENGINE MARKETING', 'Hyderabad', '<p><strong>What is SEM?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Search engine marketing which in its abbreviated form known as SEM is one of the digital marketing strategies that work towards increasing the visibility of your website in search engine result pages. It is one form of internet marketing that promotes your website by increasing your visibility in search engine results pages. If you&#39;re a business firm or a marketing company you and you&#39;re finding it difficult to cope up in the competition you can use search engine marketing or <strong><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">sem services</a> </strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>to generate more visitor to your website. The main function that SEM in digital marketing plays is it promotes a website&#39;s visibility using search engine ads, SEM campaigns, and paid searches.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SEM is important for all businesses irrespective of its size. The blog will give you a detailed description of the importance of search engine marketing particular regarding the <strong><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">importance of SEO</a> </strong>and pay per click. SEM or search engine marketing is a concept larger than you think as it involves within it both SEO and PPC. In simple words search engine marketing is a marketing strategy that involves managing a brand or website&#39;s total presence in search engine result pages. Both SEO and SEM are good for their own independent reasons, but when both of them work together they become a powerful source of sustainable success by driving revenue and sales through search engine optimization and paid search.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BENEFITS OF SEARCH ENGINE MARKETING</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.There are not one but multiple benefits that SEM in digital marketing bring to your businesses. It increases your online presence making your website more visible than your competitor&#39;s. This enhances your visibility and brand awareness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.The visibility of your website in search engine result pages and your brand&#39;s awareness among the masses generates leads and sales which helps you to make more money and stay ahead of your competitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.You can keep a check on what your competitors lack providing, and using that as a scope you can give or provide informational contents that would attract your visitors as they don&#39;t find it anywhere else.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.SEM is all about techniques like SEO and PPC working together,&nbsp; which will enhance your profit generally. You&rsquo;ll likely discover that both organic and paid marketing are worth investing in, as using them simultaneously will help your business thrive more than if you only relied on one technique and ignored your other options.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.For a long term success and growth one can really look forward to SEO whereas if you&#39;re looking for instant result then you can opt for PPC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.SEO is more affordable than any other techniques provided by different <strong><a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\">digital marketing agencies</a>.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.By working on the quality of SEO, you and your company can be ahead of other brands because due to internet and online marketing system people prefer what&#39;s unique and trending.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All the other marketing strategies have their own unique advantages but we here at ASE TECHNOLOGIES still advise our clients to have them all together in order to have a better and a greater and a more reliable result.</p>\r\n', '07-March-2022', 'search-engine-marketing-importance-of-search-engine-marketing', 'ase28.jpg', 'Search engine marketing which in its abbreviated form known as SEM is one of the digital marketing strategies that work towards increasing the visibility of your website in search engine result pages.', '', ''),
(74, 'ELEMENTS OF DIGITAL MARKETING FOR A BUSINESS', 'Hyderabad', '<p><strong>Major Components Of Digital Marketing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>No marketing plans today work without a digital strategy. The use of digital technologies by different companies to promote and sell their products or services is known as digital marketing. What digital marketing cannot do away with is digital strategy, thus, all kinds of digital marketing includes digital strategy. Digital strategies are the key features or key components of digital marketing. A marketing firm usually focuses on how a business can attract most of its potential customers or clients, retain existing customers and increase sales leads. Today, you find most of your customers online as the world is moving towards technological developments. With maximum customers being available online, digital marketing has become one of the most effective ways to interact with customers as you can now connect with them through their desired and preferred digital channels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since there are a variety of digital marketing services it becomes confusing and overwhelming to know where exactly to focus. Companies that want to stay ahead of their competitors know that they need to adopt effective and creative ways to stand out. Stand out here means to use creative and effective and also the best <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>digital marketing services</strong></a> in order to engage with potential customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To start with digital marketing, you are first required to hire the<a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"> <strong>best digital marketing agency</strong></a> that would lay out a full proof digital marketing plan. The plan would define the goals that you want to accomplish and the span of time within which you want to achieve it. The best advantage of digital marketing is that if you find your plan not working that well you&rsquo;ll be able to adjust it and make it just as it suits your benefit. There are many different key elements of digital marketing plan that you may like to know about.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Components Of Digital Marketing</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1.Content Marketing &ndash;</strong> Content marketing is one of the important components of digital marketing. It is an important strategy for attracting potential customers. Posting a regular, relatable, creative content will help establish thought leadership. It would educate your customers about how your product and service could help their problems get resolved. It would also help boosting their SEO rankings. Content can be of any type, it may include a blog, or some case studies, or other materials that would straight away reach your target audience. This is an organic way to acquire customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2.Email Marketing &ndash; </strong>Through this method direct emails are sent to the target audience or your potential clients. It involves sending of promotional messages directly to a segmented audience who can turn up to be possible customers. It is an effective approach to reach out to a particular section of audience with what they require.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.Mobile Marketing &ndash;</strong> In mobile marketing products or services of a particular company is promoted through mobile phones and other electronic devices. Advertising through text messages as well as advertising in downloaded apps is known as mobile marketing. &nbsp;However, a comprehensive mobile marketing approach also includes optimizing websites, landing pages, emails, and content for an optimal experience on mobile devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4.Advertising &ndash;</strong> Advertising is&nbsp;the techniques and practices used to bring products, services, opinions, or causes to public notice to persuade the public to respond in a certain way toward what is advertised.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These are not the only elements of digital marketing, there are more as usual. Digital marketing methods provide you and your company various ways to engage potential customers. But it is important for you to know which digital marketing agency to invest on for growth as well as to retain customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '14-March-2022', 'elements-of-digital-marketing-for-a-business', 'asetech30.jpg', 'No marketing plans today work without a digital strategy. The use of digital technologies by different companies to promote and sell their products or services is known as digital marketing', '', '');
