(118, 'Why Google My Business Is Important For Business', 'Vizag', '<p>In today&#39;s digital age, online presence is an important aspect of any business. <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>Google My Business Online</strong> </a>(GMB) is a free tool that allows businesses to create and manage their online presence across Google&#39;s search engine, maps, and other properties. It is a powerful marketing tool and <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>Google My Business optimization</strong></a> can help improve a business&#39;s visibility online, attract new customers, and provide valuable insights into customers&#39; behavior. In this blog, we will discuss Google My Business Benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Boosts Local SEO</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Local SEO is essential for brands and businesses that want to target customers in their local area. <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>Google My Business</strong></a> is an effective way to improve local SEO as it allows businesses to provide accurate information about their location, business hours, and contact information. When customers search for a product or service in their local area, Google uses the information from Google My Business listings to display relevant results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Increases Visibility</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Having a Google My Business setup can help <a href=\"https://asetechnologies.in/\"><strong>businesses increase their visibility</strong></a> on the internet. By providing relevant information about the business, like its address, phone number, and website, GMB allows businesses to appear in search results when people search for keywords related to their business. For example, if someone searches for an &quot;Italian restaurant,&quot; Google will display a list of Italian restaurants in their area along with their GMB listings, which include key information like their menu, business hours, and reviews.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Enhances Customer 